    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the Yorkshire<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> and carrots are in the oven, cut 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> pieces of <strong>tin foil</strong> approx. the size of an A3 sheet of paper and layer them over each other</p><p>Add the <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> to the middle with a few small knobs of <strong>butter</strong>, the<strong> chopped garlic</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>water</strong></p><p>Scrunch the edges of the foil around the greens to form 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2] </span>sealed parcel<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p>",
