      "instruction": "<p>Once the giant Yorkshire<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> has had an initial 12 min, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> with the carrots from the oven and add the <strong>Tenderstem parcel<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> to the other side of the tray</p><p>Remove the dish<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> from the oven and add the<strong> camembert<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>to the centre, piercing the top a few times with a sharp knife</p><p>Return both the dish<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> and tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven for a final 8 min or until the camembert has melted and the Tenderstem is tender with a slight bite</p>",
